  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.poster.avif?t=1723997928\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.webm?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.mp4?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On Mars, breakfast is no laughing matter, and whether you pour the milk or the cereal first in the bowl, there is one thing everyone can agree with: <strong>down with powdered milk!</strong><br><br>Travel to Earth and — with the help of Meadow, your assistant — catch wild cows to bring back to Mars.<br><br>So, what are you waiting for?<br>Meadow needs you! Nay, Mars needs you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A \"Sokoban\"-like puzzle game with unique mechanics<br></li><li> 100 levels<br></li><li> A gentle difficulty curve, perfect for players new to the genre<br></li><li> A lovely assistant who loves to chat<br></li><li> Tons of cows</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.poster.avif?t=1723997928\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.webm?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.mp4?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.poster.avif?t=1723997928\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.webm?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/81ae9d4e0a752ed31cc3b9632e9fc155.mp4?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On Mars, breakfast is no laughing matter, and whether you pour the milk or the cereal first in the bowl, there is one thing everyone can agree with: <strong>down with powdered milk!</strong><br><br>Travel to Earth and — with the help of Meadow, your assistant — catch wild cows to bring back to Mars.<br><br>So, what are you waiting for?<br>Meadow needs you! Nay, Mars needs you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A \"Sokoban\"-like puzzle game with unique mechanics<br></li><li> 100 levels<br></li><li> A gentle difficulty curve, perfect for players new to the genre<br></li><li> A lovely assistant who loves to chat<br></li><li> Tons of cows</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.poster.avif?t=1723997928\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.webm?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513190/extras/4c1da6b57e4a1d610c5507e383d8c62e.mp4?t=1723997928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
